stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Phase1_Telegram
    
    state Phase1_Telegram {
        [*] --> AllUsersTelegram
    }
    
    Phase1_Telegram --> Phase2_WebAdded
    
    state Phase2_WebAdded {
        [*] --> SomeUsersWeb
    }
    
    Phase2_WebAdded --> Phase3_Discord
    
    state Phase3_Discord {
        [*] --> MultiPlatform
    }
    
    Phase3_Discord --> [*]
    
    note right of Phase1_Telegram
        Phase 1: Telegram Only (MVP)<br/>Schema: NO CHANGES<br/>Data: telegram object only<br/>All users have credentials.telegram<br/>No web/discord keys yet
    end note
    
    note right of Phase2_WebAdded
        Phase 2: Web Auth Added<br/>Schema: NO CHANGES<br/>Data: telegram + web objects<br/>~20% users add credentials.web<br/>Old users still have only telegram<br/>New users might start with web
    end note
    
    note right of Phase3_Discord
        Phase 3: Discord Added (Future)<br/>Schema: NO CHANGES<br/>Data: telegram + web + discord<br/>Users have 1-3 platforms<br/>Each platform independent<br/>Primary platform = first login
    end note
